@target vue3

A single-page landing site for "kun" — an intent-driven code generator CLI tool.

The page is a vertical scroll of sections. Import and use these components in order:
  - NavBar
  - HeroSection
  - WhatIsKun
  - InstallSection
  - HowItWorks
  - WriteWhatNotHow
  - ProvidersSection
  - GitSyncContract
  - FooterSection

All components are in ./components/.

Global styles:
  - font-family: "Inter", sans-serif for body text
  - font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace for code
  - dark background (#0a0a0a), light text (#e5e5e5)
  - smooth scroll behavior
  - reset margins, padding, box-sizing: border-box
  - max content width: 960px, centered

constraints:
  - use <script setup lang="ts">
  - all global styles go in a non-scoped <style> block in App.vue
  - each section component handles its own layout
  - responsive: works on mobile and desktop
